snippet.title: Loddlenaut - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Now live on Kickstarter: https://www.loddlenaut.com/kickstarter

Play as an interstellar custodian sent to clean up a polluted ocean planet. Repurpose marine debris and take care of axolotl-like alien creatures!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1644940/Loddlenaut/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/loddlenaut
Discord: https://discord.gg/uJ8xDKTFre
Website: https://www.loddlenaut.com/

Trailer Editor - Dino Katherine | trailergoblin.com
